I've had TFA and FA Pear since my first order - Haven't been able to find a use for them .. till now!&#xD;
&#xD;
This is a great recipe! The pear note is subtle, and not too overpowering for me - The Fuji really helps out the pear in this mix - Creamy and delicious!

The 10ml sample I made didnâ€™t even last 24 hours from when I started vaping it. I was lucky enough to try the cream base from this recipe before it was released. I can confirm that this base works very well with strawberries as well as pear. I imagine you can throw whatever fruit combo you want at it and it will be good.&#xD;
&#xD;
The combo of TFA Pear and FA Pear really stands out here with a little help from FA Fuji. FA Pear and FA Fuji add just the right amount of juiciness and TFA Pear seems to bring more of the actual pear flavor. Very good.
